{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"黄浦江口放歌","authors":["戈壁舟"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":1,"day":15}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄浦江口放歌\t戈壁舟\t一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是江？是海？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是水？是天？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那朦朦胧，像幻梦似的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是云雾？是煤烟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那密密麻麻，像树林似的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是烟囱？是桅杆？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那飘飘荡荡，来往如梭的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是海鸥？是白帆？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那高高在天，重叠如山的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是楼房？是轮船？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十五年前的恶梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像就在昨天："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高楼下有多少苦难的棚户？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"港口里有多少海盗的轮船？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大马路上响着铁蹄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小弄堂中充满哀怨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里只有作奴隶的自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用愤怒垒起了座座火山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呵，我呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在江边流着仇恨的眼泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心呀，心呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了迎着风暴的海燕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从长江上游飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻过多少座恶岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡过多少个凶滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又从这儿飞向黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里烽火烧红了万里河山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕黑暗千重万重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕黑夜千年万年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呵，朝霞的火炬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将无数愤怒的眼睛点燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们黄浦江口的世界大城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早就雄立在红日的身边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三我立在摩天大楼下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楼呵，似高山一重又一重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再不感到屈辱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂起头来挺起了胸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上的野兽消灭完了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西方的豺狼无影无踪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高楼上岩壁似的窗户呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都为我展开着笑容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走在柏油马路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路呵，似大江一条又一条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再不感到压抑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着慢步自在逍遥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河里凶滩铲除干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美洲的鳄鱼早就逃跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马路上船队似的车辆呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都向我轻声地问好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呵，每一个匆匆的行人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呵，中国产业工人的老家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个面孔那样熟悉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似年年春天的鲜花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不在天山戈壁遇见过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在昆仑山脚下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不在长江大桥遇见过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在黄河三门峡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在西南的荒山密林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响着你们前进的步伐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要是工业新城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都听得见你们的乡土话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们最知道祖国有多富，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们最知道祖国有多大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楼呵，似重重山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在山中走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路呵，似条条水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在水上游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山起伏向东海之滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水奔流在黄浦江口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山是世界上的大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水是世界上的巨流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不见半殖民地的创伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不见资本主义的腐朽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能够不抚今思昔？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我立在这黄浦江口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是水？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是天？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分不清呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分不清大洋、海岸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是云雾？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是煤烟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分不清呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分不清烟囱、桅杆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是海鸥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是白帆？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分不清呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分不清高楼、轮船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座城呵是艘巨轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的航程很远很远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满载着和平、友谊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满载着威力、尊严。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二级风暴吹不斜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁的礁石碰不烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她属于祖国的舰队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驶向既定的伟大航线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年八月九日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修改于锦江"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}